title: Selena Gomez Stuns at the Premiere of Her New Show '13 Reasons Why'
text:
Selena Gomez shines in orange as she arrives at the premiere of 13 Reasons Why on Thursday night (March 30) at Paramount Pictures Studios in Los Angeles.
The 24-year-old performer was joined at the premiere by the stars of the show Dylan Minnette , Katherine Langford , and Devin Druid .
PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Selena Gomez 
Selena serves as executive producer for the Netflix show that is set to be released on this Friday (March 31).
Also spotted at the premiere were Greer Grammer , Francia Raisa , and Courtney Love .
FYI: Selena is wearing an Oscar de la Renta dress.
